This paper deals with the automated synthesis of mock HTTP services, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). The use of Symbolic Machine Learning algorithms also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the creation of customised mocks, which involves programming language concepts (cs.PL) and software design (cs.SD). Finally, the paper addresses the issue of testing, which is relevant to computer security (cs.CR).
